    "InviteText": "You've been invited to {ws}\n\nYou've been invited to join the {ws} workspace on Huly.\n\nAccept your invitation here:\n{link}\n\nThis invite link expires in {expHours} hours.\n\nIf you weren't expecting an invitation, you can safely ignore this email.",
